  "texts": [
    "As a result, in addition to 140 requirements captured by the chatbot, we identified 30 further requirements and preferences that were overlooked by the chatbot.",
    "Furthermore, out of 140 list items, 130 (92.85%) were correct, 10 were incorrect (7.15%), and 43 were invalid (12.2%).",
    "Most invalid items were texts that were generated by the chatbot or fragmented sentences.",
    "As mentioned earlier, the survey was conducted in both the experimental and control groups to evaluate service quality, enjoyment, usefulness, and ease of use of the chatbot or the survey.",
    "The results of the comparative analysis between the chatbot and survey methods demonstrated that participants rated the user experience of the chatbot more positively than the survey (see Fig. 4)."
  ],
